full_text: Case 1:20-cr-00330-PAE Document 747 Filed 08/10/22 Page 11 of 228 687 LC2Qmax1 Kane - Direct that was kept and digitized. Q. Will you turn in the binder next to you to what's been marked for identification as Government Exhibit 761? A. Yes. Q. Do you recognize this document? A. Yes, I do. Q. Without saying any names, what is it? A. This is an enrollment application for a student at the Professional Children's School. Q. Have you reviewed it prior to today? A. Yes, I have. Q. Did you compare it with the records from the Professional Children's School's database? A. Yes, I have. Q. Is it a true and accurate copy of the document at the Professional Children's School? A. Yes, it is. MR. ROHRBACH: Your Honor, the government offers Government Exhibit 761. MS. MENNINGER: Objection. Hearsay. MR. ROHRBACK: Your Honor, it's business record. THE COURT: Overruled. MS. MENNINGER: Your Honor, may I make a record or voir dire? THE COURT: You may voir dire. SOUTHERN DISTRICT REPORTERS, P.C. (212) 805-0300 DOJ-OGR-00017884
